      <li><a href="https://help.kajabi.com/en/articles/12696396-kajabi-branded-app-faqs" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-600 hover:underline">Kajabi Branded App FAQs</a> — White-label mobile app information</li>
      <li><a href="https://help.kajabi.com/en/articles/12696332-how-do-i-get-started-creating-my-own-branded-app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-600 hover:underline">Kajabi Branded App Setup</a> — Creating your branded app</li>
